# GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/health

# GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/health/db

# GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/not-exist

### Register
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Test User2",
  "email": "test2@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Me
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Update profile
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "New User Name"
}

### Change password
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "123456",
  "newPassword": "654321"
}




### Get all topics
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/topics
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>

### Get followed topics
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/user-topics
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>

### Follow topic
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/user-topics
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic_id": 1
}

### Update followed topic
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/user-topics/1
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic_id": 11
}

### Unfollow topic
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/user-topics/1
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>

### Get all papers
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/papers?page=1&limit=5&filter=all

### Get recent papers
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/papers?page=1&limit=5&filter=recent

### Get papers in last 2 days
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/papers?page=1&limit=5&filter=2days


### Lấy chi tiết paper 1
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/papers/1

### Search
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/papers/search?q=machine&page=1&limit=10

### Them muc yeu thich
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/papers/favorite/1
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>

### xoa muc yeu thich
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/papers/favorite/1
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>

### Lay muc yeu thich
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/favorites?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>

### Lay danh sach thong bao
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/notifications?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>

### Lay thong bao chua doc
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/notifications?page=1&limit=10&unread_only=true
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>

### Notification SSE stream - dung tren browser/EventSource
# GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/notifications/stream?token=<access_token>

### Danh dau 1 thong bao da doc
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/v1/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>

### Danh dau tat ca thong bao da doc
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/v1/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>

### Internal push notification tu DB pipeline sang BE
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/internal/notifications/push
x-internal-api-secret: <internal_api_secret>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event": "NEW_NOTIFICATION",
  "notification_ids": [1],
  "notification_count": 1
}
